content:
This component renders a pricing section for the DocMed application. It displays different pricing tiers, allows users to toggle between monthly and yearly billing cycles, and provides a call to action for upgrading or contacting sales.

## Key Exports

*   `PricingSection`: The main React component that renders the pricing section.

## Components

*   `BillingCycleToggle`: A UI component to switch between 'monthly' and 'yearly' billing.
*   `PricingCard`: Renders an individual pricing tier card.
*   `ContactModal`: A modal for users to contact sales for enterprise plans.

## `PricingSection` Props

This component does not accept any props.

## `PricingCard` Props

*   `tier`: An object conforming to `TierConfig` defining the pricing tier details.
*   `cycle`: The currently selected `BillingCycle` ('monthly' or 'yearly').

## Usage Example

```tsx
import { PricingSection } from '@/components/ui/pricing-section';

function App() {
  return (
    <div>
      {/* Other components */}
      <PricingSection />
      {/* Other components */}
    </div>
  );
}

export default App;
```
